----------------
Security Tab:
- Seed phrase generation
- Seed phrase restore
- Backup/restore ZIP
- Danger Zone reset
- Encryption status

API Key Manager Tab:
- Provider list
- Add/edit API keys
- Save → triggers encryption
- Load → decrypts config.enc

